{"tid":893652,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無中坑入黎一齊講下7 80年代既野","createTime":"2018-11-07T20:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T13:38:39.000Z","uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bd776d1a65f68148e50ea7c27f5a577f96e5c5","tid":893652,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:42:23.000Z","msg":"我72年既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成廿年無去過戲院 多數租碟<br />\n<br />\n早兩日個女陪我去睇發哥套無雙我先知原來而家d戲院間到咁細間 (個女話已經叫大院 係九龍灣)<br />\n<br />\n我諗起以前大光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  翡翠明珠果d勁大間有兩層坐滿哂午夜場<br />\n<br />\n真係好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5b322cc924955b343fd9509ecb80fad174981e","tid":893652,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:43:10.000Z","msg":"1872"},{"pid":"01a50ea52a66946b3bc4d08e0407abf0805243f7","tid":893652,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d5b322cc924955b343fd9509ecb80fad174981e","tid":893652,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:43:10.000Z","msg":"1872"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:45:17.000Z","msg":"1972 45歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86fe8b6cf90f60ceb1e71bdbdb3f95575f9acca","tid":893652,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01a50ea52a66946b3bc4d08e0407abf0805243f7","tid":893652,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d5b322cc924955b343fd9509ecb80fad174981e","tid":893652,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:43:10.000Z","msg":"1872"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:45:17.000Z","msg":"1972 45歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"去觀塘戲院睇咸片仲好啦"},{"pid":"74fa0acead65b58a8b0e9243c209c22b2096accc","tid":893652,"uid":214590,"l